title: Why the FBI Indicting Biden is Not What it Seems with Miranda Devine
itunes:title: Why the FBI Indicting Biden is Not What it Seems with Miranda Devine
description:
While conservatives everywhere are cheering about the FBI finally having enough evidence to indict Hunter Biden, Charlie spends the full hour giving listeners all of the reasons why they shouldn’t be, and he goes back in time to when he predicted exactly what’s unfolding with this so-called ‘justice.’ Conservatives should not fall into the trap of the FBI trying to clean up their image, coincidentally right before midterms, and Miranda Devine, author of ‘Laptop From Hell’ is on the show to give listeners the facts behind this leak, the Biden’s involvement, and more.

Support the show: http://www.charliekirk.com/support
